description: This file defines internal API function prototypes for the Slap Var Entity Object within the Service Logic Aggregation Plane (SLAP) framework. It includes functions for resetting the object, getting and setting variable syntax, content type, and usage type.

methods.name: SlapVeoReset
methods.description: Resets the internal state of the Slap Var Entity Object.

methods.name: SlapVeoGetVarSyntax
methods.description: Retrieves the syntax type of a variable.

methods.name: SlapVeoGetVarContentType
methods.description: Retrieves the content type of a variable.

methods.name: SlapVeoSetVarContentType
methods.description: Sets the content type of a variable.

methods.name: SlapVeoGetVarUsageType
methods.description: Retrieves the usage type of a variable.

methods.name: SlapVeoSetVarUsageType
methods.description: Sets the usage type of a variable.
